        "width": 681.77,
        "height": 226.77
      },
      "text": "Dose-proportional increase from 50 to 150 mg and less than dose-proportionally for higher doses of JNJ-1802. \nTerminal half-life: 6.3 to 9.2 days; accumulation factor: from 4.3 to 7.3 after 10 days and 14.6 after 31 days. \nRenal elimination of JNJ-1802 was very limited (<0.001% of the dose).",
      "style": {
        "font_size_pt": 14.0
      },
      "z": 0,
      "placeholder_id": null,
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "element_id": "shp14",
